4
00:00:20,640 --> 00:00:21,960
is also unparalleled in the world.

5
00:00:21,960 --> 00:00:22,800
Indeed.

6
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:24,080
This San Xiang Tea House

7
00:00:24,080 --> 00:00:25,720
