8
00:00:25,960 --> 00:00:27,480
Marvelous, marvelous.

9
00:00:28,880 --> 00:00:30,240
I wonder what kind of man

10
00:00:30,240 --> 00:00:31,960
would be worthy of the beautiful Qing Dai.

11
00:00:31,960 --> 00:00:33,240
Such unparalleled beauty.

12
00:00:42,640 --> 00:00:43,320
May I ask, miss,

13
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:45,200
