14
00:00:46,960 --> 00:00:48,240
I am indeed, Qing Dai at your service.

15
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:51,720
Then, are these purses and pastries

16
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:53,840
items from your shop?

17
00:01:02,480 --> 00:01:04,920
This pastry is indeed from my shop.

18
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:08,920
However, this pouch...

19
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:10,039
I've never seen it before.

20
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:19,640
And who might this gentleman be?

21
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:21,360
This is my...

22
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:23,160
I am Colonel Xiao's fellow disciple.

23
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:24,039
Mo Ze.

24
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:26,320
I've just been assigned to the patrol division.

25
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,080
I found this pastry quite special,

26
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:29,400
so I followed the aroma here.

27
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:31,200
Ah, so you're Colonel Mo from the patrol division.

28
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:33,000
I mustn't be remiss in my hospitality then.

29
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:34,240
This way to the private room, sir.

30
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,520
Hey.

31
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:42,759
A private room for one hour, fifteen taels.

32
00:01:42,759 --> 00:01:43,680
Fifteen taels?

33
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:46,960
This is robbery!

34
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:48,360
My monthly salary is only ten taels.

35
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:50,680
Lord Mo, it's an honor to have you visit on your first day in office.

36
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:52,759
It's truly our tea house's privilege.

37
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,360
Here's our Baozhuanxiang incense for you.

38
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,800
Baozhuanxiang?

39
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:59,200
When burned, this incense resembles ancient seal script,

40
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:01,320
as if dragons and phoenixes are dancing.

41
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,320
That's how it got its name.

42
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:08,639
The Green Ghost thief appeared last night.

43
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,560
I wonder if the young lady has seen...

44
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:19,079
The ancients spoke of the ten virtues of appreciating incense.

45
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,800
It has the virtue of purifying the body and mind,

46
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:22,800
and finding tranquility amidst leisure.

47
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:25,720
Master Mo's heart today

48
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,280
seems far from tranquil.

49
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,040
Master Xiao,

50
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:34,240
Master Jia asked me to deliver this paper to Colonel Mo.

51
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:35,800
My senior is busy.

52
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,800
You can give it to me.

53
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,680
Master Jia says you should strengthen your vigilance.

54
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:40,840
I'll take my leave now.

55
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:48,720
The Four Beauties screen, easily obtained.

56
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:51,000
The Blue Demon Bandit.

57
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:53,520
I also know that Yi De is deeply moved by spirits and gods.

58
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:55,800
I wonder, miss,

59
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,720
do you think this bandit is a demon or a god?

60
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:00,280
My knowledge is limited,

61
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:02,280
I can only interpret based on the words.

62
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:05,000
Since he calls himself the Blue Demon Bandit,

63
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,880
he should be a demon, I suppose.

64
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,360
You hiccup when you're nervous.

65
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,960
And you say you're not lying.

66
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:35,400
I truly feel

67
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,240
Boss Qing Dai,

68
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:39,000
you are very similar to a sister I've lost contact with.

69
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:50,680
I wonder if Boss Qing Dai remembers this scar.

70
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,400
Don't hit sister.

71
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,600
General Mo is so affectionate.

72
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:13,200
If I were that old friend of yours,

73
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,160
I probably wouldn't have the heart to deceive you.

74
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,840
This teahouse is full of all sorts of people.

75
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:25,880
I wonder if Qing Dai, the owner,

76
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:27,280
has ever heard the customers mention

77
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:28,320
the Situ mansion

78
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:29,920
and the great fire from ten years ago.

79
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,760
Mother.

80
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,200
Mother.

81
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:39,720
Mother.

82
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:49,040
Colonel Mo doesn't seem to be here for tea tasting today.

83
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:50,800
It's more like he's here to investigate a case and search for someone.

84
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:53,240
If you suspect me of anything,

85
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:55,000
