88
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,360
Madam Qing Dai, please don't misunderstand.

89
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,840
I may be a few years older than you, sir,

90
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:08,160
but I'm not yet desperate to get married.

91
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,680
This lotus tea

92
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,480
leaves a lingering fragrance

93
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,120
