94
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:22,680
Senior Brother,

95
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:27,560
This was sent by Inspector Jia's messenger.

96
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:28,600
They want us to strengthen our vigilance.

97
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:36,600
Senior Brother,

98
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,040
