132
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,840
The owner of Sanxiang Tea House.

133
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:07,920
She looks like Yun'er.

134
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:10,960
I see.

135
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:13,840
